snippet.title: HABROMANIA Gameplay Sneak Peek 3 - 1st minute of gameplay
snippet.description:
A sneak peek of the first minute of HABROMANIA gameplay (minus the cutscenes and UI screens!) 

After a long, long, long fall, Alice wakes at the bottom of a hole. She's alive- though she honestly has no earthly idea how she managed to survive falling half a thousand meters- and now has to figure out a way back to the surface. It's... easier said than done.

PS. Toska Studios is our game dev studio, comprised of me and the rest of the HABROMANIA dev team!

PSS. The dialogue sound is just a placeholder and will be changed in the full release :)
